latestIgtvVideos.caption:
1. Cleanse the face with organic Acne control Face wash 
2. Cleanse the face and unfold the mask from the sachet. Gently apply on a clean face with protective film on the outside of your face. Adjust the mask to the contours of your face leave it on for 10-15mins. Gently remove the mask . @oh_ind 
3. Face Elixer serum, take 3-4 drops of radiance face elixer serum on your palm, apply over the face with fingertips and gently massage onto the skin until fully absorbed. To be used twice a day. 
4. Face Elixer Cream, massage a small amount of Radiance face elixer cream in upward stroke on face and neck using fingertips! @oh_ind @punjab_sales

“Sapne chhote ho ya bade, unhe poora krne k lie waqt aur jazba dono chaiye. Bahut log raaste mein thak ke ruk jaate hain, apne khwabon ko chor dete hain bas thodi door pehle. Par sach yeh hai, jo cheezein waqayi kaabil-e-tareef hoti hain, unhe banne mein waqt lagta hai – kabhi kabhi saalon lag jatey hain. Har naya din ek nayi ummeed le kar aata hai, jo dheere dheere zindagi mein sukoon aur motivation sa lagne lagta hai. Agar aaj thak gaye ho, ruk jao – lekin bas ek break lo, sapne mat chhodo. Aaj jo tumhare liye mushkil lag raha hai, kal wahi tumhari jeet ki kahani banega.

Mainne apna makeup career apne room se start kiya tha. Jab papa ne meri mehnat aur khuloosi dekhi, unhone khud mera studio banwaya, har trah se poore studio me vision sab unka rha, interior exterior sab khud ka socha hua kia ho. Unka har waqt support hona ek dua ki tarah tha-har manzil aise lagti thi jaise papa ne humare saamne rakh di ho, bas uthani thi. Unke saath humne sirf studio nahi, ek academy bhi khadi ki, Alhumdulillah.
Lekin phir ek din papa ka saath chhutt gaya. Lagta tha jaise duniya ruk gayi ho. Na koi raasta dikhta tha, na koi sahara, na hi koi motivation bachi thi, Bas ek cheez thi, apni maa ka sahara banna hai, ghar chalana hai aur sapne dekhna nahi chhodna. Papa ka sapna tha ek shandaar makeup studio kholne ka, lekin jab resources aur sources kuch bhi nahi bache toh har cheez mushkil ho gayi.

Us waqt ALLAH ne meri badi behen ko hamare har trah se sambhalne ki salahiyat di, vo apna dykh dard sab chorkr, sirf hanari zindagi smbhalne me lag gyi.. Saba api ghar ka sahara bani aur har kaam khud sambhala. Hum dono ne milkar studio ka har kona, har chhoti chhoti cheez dil se pasand ki. Bahut galtiyan hui, nuksaan uthaye, aur dil bhi toote. Raaton ko bina khaye-piye kaam kiya. Har breakdown se nikalna ek jang thi, jo lafzon mein bayan nahi ki ja sakti.

Aur meri behen, Nida api, jo personal reasons ki wajah se hamare saath nahi khadi aaj, unka emotional aur mental support har waqt hamare saath tha. Unka interior decorator hone ka talent ek blessing ban gaya—unka guidance aur ideas ki wajah se studio design karna humare liye aasaan ho gaya. Nida api, we missed you so much. Aapki duaen aur support ne humein har kadam par hausla diya.

Papa ke jaane ke baad lagta tha jaise zindagi se sab kuch chhin gaya ho. Roz uthna ek routine tha, lekin jeena nahi lagta tha. Har vo cheez jo insaan ko emotional aur mental level pe tod sakti hai, hamare saath hui. Lekin ek cheez thi jo kabhi nahi chhodi-sapne dekhna. Mere sapne mere papa ke sapno ka ek hissa the, aur meri family har kadam par mera saath deti rahi.

Read more in the pinned comment.

Every single time I saw my dad praying, he’d say “Allah kabhi kisi ka bhi mohtaaj na karay” Now when I’m mature enough to understand it, I realize this is the best dua you can make for this wordly life🥺🤲🏻
